==演化==
短面熊屬於[[眼鏡熊亞科|眼鏡熊亞科]]，演化自出現於晚[[中新世|中新世]]的{{link-en|Plionarctos}}。在[[南北美洲生物大遷徙|南北美洲生物大遷徙]]時，眼鏡熊亞科入侵南美洲，並且演化出[[細齒巨熊|細齒巨熊]]以及現存的[[眼鏡熊|眼鏡熊]]。雖然對短面熊的早期歷史所知甚少，牠後來於80萬年前{{link-en|堪薩冰川作用時期|Kansan glaciation}}廣泛分布於北美洲。

[[巨型短面熊|巨型短面熊]]（''Arctodus simus''）最早出現在80萬年前中[[更新世|更新世]]時期的[[北美洲|北美洲]]，分布範圍大致從[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]至[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]<ref>C. S. Churcher, A. V. Morgan, and L. D. Carter. 1993. ''Arctodus simus from the Alaskan Arctic Slope''. Canadian Journal of Earth Sciences 30(5):1007-1013, collected by A. V. Morgan</ref><ref>M. L. Cassiliano. 1999. Biostratigraphy of Blancan and Irvingtonian mammals in the Fish Creek-Vallecito Creek section, southern California, and a review of the Blancan-Irvingtonian boundary. Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology 19(1):169-186</ref>。巨型短面熊約在 11,600 年前絕種，化石最早發現於[[加州|加州]][[沙斯塔縣|沙斯塔縣]]的 Potter Creek Cave<ref>COPE, E. D. 1879. The cave bear of California. American Naturalist, 13:791.</ref>。巨型短面熊是目前北美洲已知體型最大的陸域[[肉食性|肉食性]][[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]（次於[[細齒巨熊|細齒巨熊]]）。一具巨型短面熊的化石在[[印第安納州|印第安納州]]的[[羅切斯特_(印第安納州)|羅切斯特]]出土<ref name = "willard">{{cite web | url = https://www.fultoncountyhistory.org/shirley-willard-writings | title = Rochester's Giant Bear Gets Famous | last = Willard | first = S. | website = fultoncountyhistory.org | access-date = 2017-07-17 | archive-date = 2018-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181018122333/https://www.fultoncountyhistory.org/shirley-willard-writings | dead-url = no }}</ref>，為目前所發現最完整的全身骨骼化石，樣本目前保存於[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的[[菲爾德自然史博物館|菲爾德自然史博物館]]<ref name = "willard"/>。

倭短面熊（''Arctodus pristinus''）分布於較南方的地區，包括北[[德克薩斯州|德州]]至東[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]、[[阿瓜斯卡連特斯州|阿瓜斯卡連特斯州]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]<ref>I. Ferrusquia-Villafranca. 1978. Bol Univ Nac Aut Mex Inst Geol 101:193-321</ref>。並且在[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]有大量化石出土，最早的樣本出自[[吉爾克里斯特縣_(佛羅里達州)|吉爾克里斯特郡]]。

==描述==
根據最近的研究，6具巨型短面熊的樣本中有2具估計個體體重約{{convert|900|kg|lb|abbr=on}}，其中最重的為{{convert|957|kg|lb|abbr=on}}的編號 UVP 015 樣本，這代表著這樣體型的個體其實比之前預估的還常見<ref name=Figueiridio_et_al_2010>{{cite journal|title=Demythologizing Arctodus simus, the 'short-faced' long-legged and predaceous bear that never was|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|year=2010|volume=30|issue=1|pages=262–275|doi=10.1080/02724630903416027|url=https://dx.doi.org/10.1080/02724630903416027|author=Figueirido|display-authors=etal}}</ref>。巨型短面熊後腳站起來時全高 {{convert|2.4|-|3.0|m|ft|abbr=on}}<ref name="Simus">{{cite web |url=http://www.adfg.alaska.gov/index.cfm?adfg=wildlifenews.view_article&articles_id=232&issue_id=41 |title=The Biggest Bear ... Ever |author=Nancy Sisinyak |publisher=''Alaska Fish and Wildlife News'' |accessdate=2008-01-12 |archive-date=2012-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121230121051/https://www.adfg.alaska.gov/index.cfm?adfg=wildlifenews.view_article&articles_id=232&issue_id=41 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而較大型的個體全高則可達 {{convert|3.4|-|3.7|m|ft|abbr=on}}。四足行走時，肩高為 {{convert|1.5|-|1.8|m|ft|abbr=on}}，可以與人平視<ref>{{cite web|title=Yukon Beringia Interpretive Centre|url=http://www.beringia.com/research/bear.html|accessdate=17 April 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331005507/http://www.beringia.com/research/bear.html|archivedate=31 March 2014|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=North American Bear Center|url=https://www.bear.org/website/bear-pages/extinct-short-faced-bear.html|work=Extinct Short-faced Bear|accessdate=17 April 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921060910/https://www.bear.org/website/bear-pages/extinct-short-faced-bear.html|archive-date=2018-09-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Brown|first=Gary|title=The Bear Almanac, 2nd: A Comprehensive Guide to the Bears of the World|date=December 3, 2013|publisher=Lyons Press|isbn=978-0762788064|page=8|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5B1VAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA8#v=onepage&q&f=false|access-date=2018-10-22|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129072331/http://books.google.com/books?id=5B1VAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA8#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[美國|美國]][[密蘇里州|密蘇里州]]的{{link-en|河階洞|Riverbluff Cave}}中，科學家在{{convert|4.6|m|ft|abbr=on}}高的牆面上發現熊的爪印，這代表著短面熊站起來的高度可以達到{{convert|3.7|m|ft|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Bear Claw Marks|url=http://www.riverbluffcave.com/gallery/rec_id/104/type/1|work=Riverbluff Cave - The Official Website|accessdate=17 April 2014|archive-date=2018-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181101211956/http://www.riverbluffcave.com/gallery/rec_id/104/type/1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cave Animals|url=http://www.riverbluffcave.com/category/cave_animals|work=Riverbluff Cave - The Official Website|accessdate=17 April 2014|archive-date=2018-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022232452/http://www.riverbluffcave.com/category/cave_animals|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

